AUTHORS:

- Jeroen Demeyer (2015-04-10): initial version, :trac:`18052`.

EXAMPLES::

    sage: def the_answer():
    ....:     return 42
    sage: f = pari(the_answer)
    sage: f()
    42

    sage: cube = pari(lambda i: i^3)
    sage: cube.apply(range(10))
    [0, 1, 8, 27, 64, 125, 216, 343, 512, 729]
"""

